                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5702" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0284</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8403 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长舟破浪行，东方曙景新：武汉新东方的组织发展之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Large Boat Breaks through the Waves, and the Dawn of  the East Is Appearing:the Road of New Oriental’s Organizational Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑耀洲，尤咏洁，张安娜，薛涵方，文豪，王淑红，刘友斌</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉新东方</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">教育培训；新东方；组织发展；组织发展阶段</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Education and Training; New Oriental; Organizational Development; Organization Development Stages</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着武汉经济快速发展，教育培训行业增长强劲、前景可观，线上线下机构同台竞技，市场竞争愈演愈烈，作为领军企业的武汉新东方产生了前所未有的紧迫感。然而，公司内部存在的诸多问题却牵制了其组织发展。本案例描述了近三年武汉新东方组织发展的全过程。首先，案例讲述了一次由人才调离引发的人才危机，以及化解这一危机的拆分事件。接着，案例展现了在拆分事件后，武汉新东方是如何从人才、组织和业务三方面进行反思，并通过更为细致的人才盘点、组织盘点和业务复盘，发现内部存在人才储备不足、资源利用不充分、运营效率较低、战略未落地等问题。然后，案例描述了武汉新东方是如何推进战略落地，对校区进行划分，完善运营闭环，增加人才储备和提升人才能力的。最后，案例呈现了疫情期间武汉新东方快速感知环境变化、利用机会吸引人才、重构与优化组织资源的过程。本案例旨在通过一个真实完整的案例，还原组织发展实践的全过程，加深学生对组织发展相关理论的深入理解，为企业的组织发展实践提供参考。 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With rapid economic development of Wuhan, the education and training industry has promising prospects, online and offline institutions compete fiercely. As a leading company, Wuhan New Oriental has created a sense of urgency. However, many problems within the company have hindered its development. This case describes the entire development process of Wuhan New Oriental. First, the case describes a talent crisis caused by a talent transfer, and a split event to resolve this crisis. Then, the case shows how it reflected on the talents, organization and business, and through more detailed inventories and review, it found that there were insufficient talent reserves and utilization, low operational efficiency, and failure to implement strategies. Then, the case describes how it promoted the implementation of the strategy, divided the campus, improved the closed-loop operation, increased the talent reserve and improved the talent capacity. Finally, the case shows it’s rapid perception of environmental changes, the use of opportunities to attract talents, and the reconstruction of organizational resources during COVID-19. This case aims to restore the entire process of organizational development, deepen students’ understanding of the relevant theories, and provide references of the organization development practice for the enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《员工培训与发展》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
